####################################
#
#   What is the openITCOCKPIT installer:
#
####################################

This shell script installs openITCOCKPIT. For this purpose it downloads or uses a previously downladed installation package from Nezztek to make all the necessary 3rd party Tools and the openITCOCKPIT-Frontend available to the installer.

####################################
#
#   License:
#
####################################

This script is released under the GPLv2
Details about this license can be found at http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html

####################################
#
#   System requirements:
#
####################################

The installer should work with the following Linux derivatives

- Debian 6.x
- Ubuntu 10.04
- Ubuntu 11.10
- Ubuntu 14.04
- SLES 11
- openSUSE 11.2
- openSUSE 12

####################################
#
#   Installation:
#
####################################

Just provide the execution right to the install.sh file and run the install.sh.
After the start of the installer just follow the instructions

